'''Rogue Twelve''' was the [[Callsign/Legends|call sign]] used by certain fighter pilots of [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]].

The pilots who have used the call sign include:
*[[Dash Rendar/Legends|Dash Rendar]] ([[3 ABY/Legends|3 ABY]])<ref name="Essential Guide to Warfare">''[[The Essential Guide to Warfare]]''</ref>
*[[Standro Jcir]] ([[4 ABY/Legends|4 ABY]])<ref name="XWRS:ItES">[[X-Wing Rogue Squadron 24|''X-Wing Rogue Squadron'' 24]]</ref>
*[[Andoorni Hui]] ([[6 ABY/Legends|6.5 ABY]])<ref name="XW:RS">''[[X-Wing: Rogue Squadron]]''</ref>
*[[Aril Nunb]] (6.5-[[7 ABY/Legends|7 ABY]])<ref name="XW:WG">''[[X-Wing: Wedge's Gamble]]''</ref><ref name="XW:TKT">''[[X-Wing: The Krytos Trap]]''</ref>
*[[Inyri Forge]] (7-[[9 ABY/Legends|9 ABY]])<ref name="XW:SC">''[[X-Wing: Solo Command]]''</ref><ref name="XW:IR">''[[X-Wing: Isard's Revenge]]''</ref>
*[[Tik (Rogue Squadron)|Tik]] ([[25 ABY/Legends|25 ABY]])<ref name="NJO:DT">''[[The New Jedi Order: Dark Tide I: Onslaught]]''</ref>
*[[Anni Capstan]] (25 ABY)<ref name="NJO:DT" />
*[[Lensi]] ([[26 ABY/Legends|26]]-[[29 ABY/Legends|29 ABY]])<ref name="NJO:EoV">''[[The New Jedi Order: Edge of Victory II: Rebirth]]''</ref><ref name="CSWE">''[[The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia]]''</ref>

